        "description": "<p>This field is included for legacy purposes; use the <code>role_name</code> field instead. The <code>maintain</code>\nrole is mapped to <code>write</code> and the <code>triage</code> role is mapped to <code>read</code>. To determine the role\nassigned to the collaborator, use the <code>role_name</code> field instead, which will provide the full\nrole name, including custom roles.</p>",
